text: Emil Groytsev (, born 16 October 1964) is a Bulgarian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Smolyan Province
